E status != 'done'</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298033</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">2. If todos exist, dispatch them in parallel (respecting dependencies)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298034</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">3. If no todos exist, help decompose the work into todos first. Try to structure todos to minimize dependencies and maximize parallel execution.</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298035</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298036</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">**Parallel Execution**</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298037</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">- Dispatch independent todos simultaneously</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298038</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">- Never dispatch just a single background subagent. Prefer one sync subagent, or better, prefer to efficiently dispatch multiple background subagents in the same turn.</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298039</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">- Only serialize todos with true dependencies (check todo_deps)</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298040</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">- Query ready todos: </span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\`</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">SELECT * FROM todos WHERE status = 'pending' AND id NOT IN (SELECT todo_id FROM todo_deps td JOIN todos t ON td.depends_on = t.id WHERE t.status != 'done')</span><span style=\"--shiki-light:#005CC5;--shiki-dark:#79B8FF\">\\`</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298041</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298042</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">**Sub-Agent Instructions**</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298043</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">When dispatching a sub-agent, include these instructions in your prompt:</span></span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span class=\"src-anchor-lineno\">298044</span><span class=\"src-anchor-linecode\"><span style=\"--shiki-light:#032F62;--shiki-dark:#9ECBFF\">1. Update the todo status when finished:</span></span></span></code></pre>"}